messages.content: Normally Cerises mindscape is a rave but....ever since she was taken over by Darkness it was all muted and quiet. She was currently laying facedown on the floor, a muffled caramelldansen playing from the speakers. She groaned and rolled onto her back, staring up into the void of darkness above her.
Well- she didnt get to be here for long.
Shale blinks. "What the hell."
Cerise is once again, vibing on the floor.
"Cerise. Cerise?" Shale looks back the opposite direction. "Welp. Shes dead." Shale splats on the floor next to her, face down.
She turns her head to look at her "Shale???? What are you doing here????" She sits up, obviously confused
"Didn't mean to come here. Sorry." Shale mumbles, muffled from. Well. Being facedown on the floor.
"Its alright..." She chuckled a bit "Sorry...my....mindscape is all too exciting....it....changed after I got possessed. Look up."
"Ooo. Pretty." Shale rolls over.
"I....dont like it....it just makes me think that entity is still there....I know its not but....its hard to not think about what happened..."
"Have you tried this?" Shale waves her arms dramatically. "Let there be light!" She pauses. "Worth a shot."
"Let....me try...Uh....let there be light!" She shouted this. It worked, a little. "Huh....Well its an improvement...."
"Cerise, do you know what this means?" Shale rolls over and shakes her shoulder excitedly. "You're *god*!"
She giggled, tail wagging a bit "Mmm Im so glad I met you...."
Shale grins. "I would be glad I met me too! I would be fine company."
She giggled more, standing up and stretching "You wanna experience a rave?"
"Hell yeah! I was in jail too much to go to one as Jolyne."
She clapped her hands, the strobe lights coming on and the other lights going out. Music that Cherry liked began to play and Shale was decked out with glow sticks now
"Nice!" Shale grins at her.
"Thank you~!" She grinned
Shale hums along to the song, smiling.
Cerise just Gets Down. Shes pretty happy
Shale doesn't know how to dance... so she watches Cerise happily.
Shes just in her zone having fun
Shale grins at her.
Eventually she gets tired and lays on the floor again
Shale lies on top of her. "You're in your element with raves..."
"Well, yeah. They where the one escape I had in the human world after the crash..." she hummed
"Awesome..."
"I wonder if I can still menace...."
"I can." Shale demonstrates.
She claps "Nice nice!!!"
Shale grins. "Still got the touch."
"Have you ever rollerbladed?"
"Would you like to learn?"
She smiled "Ill teach you when I wake up k?"
"Okay. When do you want to head up?" Shale smiles.
"Mmm Im not sure....im...still pretty exhausted from being possessed and having to fight against it..." she hummed
"Well, we know what to do if you get possessed next time.... Do you think the crystal has reached anywhere in space yet?"
"Probably...." she played with her hair a bit
"....She might find Kars, or stop thinking." Shale sits up and puts on a mock dramatic voice. "*Eventually, Darkness stopped thinking.*"
She snickered "Hell yeah."
"Heh." Shale lies back down again.
Cerise cuddles her a bit
Shale hums happily. "Where do you think I could get a suit of armour? Or a sword?"
"Hmm.....I dunno..."
"...I'd probably need to learn how to swordfight, but that's easy. Can't be much different from a staff or a big stick, right? It's just sharper."
((Shale is very, very wrong. They're balanced completely differently. She's going to fall on her face))
"Hm.....Do.....you wanna see if Unis sleeping??? Maybe we can get her to come vibe here???"
"Sure! I'm gonna search up places I can get an armour and sword in the void anyway on my tesseract anyway when I'm back in my body."
She nodded "Alright then, see you in the waking world?" She smiled
"See you! I have this cool new exit thing. Watch as I ascend." Shale spreads her arms and levitates, glowing and grinning at Cerise. Then she goes further upwards and disappears.
She claps in amazement before waking herself up

Shes here. Again. The rave was kinda....dulled and stuff was broken. All due to her relapse. "......Ugh...." She didnt like it "Gotta.....try and fix this..I guess...." She sighed and began to try and put her mindscape back together.
Its not working too well....shes...feeling isolated. Shes scared....She hates this feeling....
Then she hears it. The noise. The scene. The one thing she hates the most. Its her mindscape monster.
She tries to hide. She has to hide. She cant deal with this. Shes so scared
The noises play via the speakers. She can't drown it out.
The crash is playing over and over on a projecter.
Cerise is crying
The monster is getting closer
Cerise is full on sobbing now
The monster is right over her.
Now would be the best time to help her
Gemi is here
And she starts to punch the shit out of the monster
It lets out a horrible screeching noise. Like tires screeching on the road. It tries to defend itself
"LEAVE HER ALONE!"
Many punches
It runs off, leaving Cerise a sobbing mess
Gemi hugged her
She hugged back, sobbing
"I'm here Cerise...I'm sorry for what happened..."
"I-im so scared...I-I want it to stop....I-I dont wanna b-be alone..."
"I'm here...it's gonna be ok..."
She keeps sobbing, the cracks becoming visible in her mindscape
@Iris
"Ohnonononono-" gemi is starting to panic
She takes a deep breath
"Cerise...tell me what's wrong."

"I-Im scared.....I-I feel like I can never h-help....I-its always sh-shake or u-uni helping....An-and I ha-had to be.....pi-pinned down....s-so I didnt h-hurt myself....I-I feel....useless....pathetic even....." She whimpered
"You're not useless for not knowing how to help...you can't always help everyone. It's not your job."
Her arms hurt. She wanted to hurt them more. "I-I want these u-urges to stop.....I-I wanna look be-beautiful for our wedding......I-I dont w-want to see m-my scars....."
"You always look beautiful...I wish you wouldn't do this to yourself."
She just kept sobbing into the others shoulder "Wh-when you s-saw me using an i-ice cube ....o-on my wr-wrists.....I-It was to st-stop m-myself.....fr-from ||cutting||...."
Gemi didn't know what to say
//I don't know what to say and I'm kind of panicking
(Just letting her talk helps
(Shes gonna calm down after just having someone listen to her
(She jjst really needed to vent
Gemi just pats her on the back
Eventually she starts to calm down "Th-Thank you for listening...." She smiled "I-I needed that....."
"What do you say we wake up and I make you something?"
She nodded "I would like that..."
Cerise is here and laying on the ground, staring up at the ceiling
She has no idea why the fusion made her feel uncomfortable. Was it cause she felt like if she kissed them she would be kissing Venor too?
She has to face this problem of hers
